                     <interp inst="t18210606-39-person465" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner in Burnham-place.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I know nothing of it.</p>
